hough they have a social life, they bring their flawed emotional state with them in public. Generally, they are of a fragile disposition and are easily insulted. From every word they take a meaning that was not intended, seeing in it a meaning intended ag
ainst them. They are easily demoralised and offended. At the least provocation, their eyes well-up with tears, and they may even weep secretly.
